<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><lyrics>[V1]
 1. Jordan luipi gal lehlam ah,
 Kanaan gam nuom lam ka thil leh,
 Ka lungdeih changbang ka khente,
 Vanmi-laia buolin ka mui.

[V2]
 Hukdampa hehpihna lopi,
 Pakin a thisana tatte;
 Nawpna pak hawih lunna gamah,
 Angel tawh laituol leng hitiu.

[V3]
 2. Enun, a hinkhuo a dangtai,
 Gam lopi tuollai a lengte;
 Lungkhamna kipahna asuok,
 Thihna kumsawt hinnan a theng.

[V4]
 3. Lei dahum ke'nlam - bang pelin,
 Lungkham lusu'n kahna pelin,
 Ngilhloh lungtuok luonthi nula.
 Chang bang khente tui bang kigawm.

[V5]
 4. Lei dahum cheng cheng thuok zo a,
 Hukdampa mina liengvai te;
 Thagau chawlhna nuom a chang tau,
 Kumkhaw sawtin chawl den tanau.</lyrics>
<title>Thihna Jordan Galah !</title>
<author>Kamlala</author>
<hymn_number>181</hymn_number>
</song>